metadata.name: Bapes Clan
metadata.description: Bapes is the first metavestor club, that exclusively empowers crypto native companies, forged in the metaverse. Bapes was founded by successful bumans with super-high diversity backgrounds working in a myriad of divergent industries. Every Bapes club member is considered a metavestor partner, and therefore an owner, in all the companies that the Bapes clan, as a collective, votes to invest in, from the Bapes fund. Members of the Bapes club will enjoy VIP access to the high-end Bapes Club House, built in the metaverse, to mingle and connect with highly successful VIP business owners and founders of unicorn companies, celebrities, artists, content creators, and more.
